  "text": "We will construct now the Thom class in the Fredholm picture. If X is a proper G-manifold, by Theorem 2.3 in [CITATION_1] for every x ∈ X there is a open neighbourhood U of x contractible to the orbit of x in X ⋊ G with action of the isotropy group G x such that there is a Lie groupoid isomorphism",
